        <div type="letter">
            <div type="text">
                <opener>
                    <placeName><hi rend="print">Herbarium of Harvard University, | Botanic Garden, Cambridge, Mass.</hi></placeName>
                    <date>May 22 <hi rend="print">187</hi>7</date>
                    <salute>My Dear Darwin</salute>
                </opener>
                <div type="transcription">
                     
<p>I asked my good correspondent Prof. Bessey to see if <hi rend="underline">Lithospermum</hi> <hi rend="underline">longiflorum</hi> (= angustifolium) being cleistogenous later, is, like its relatives, also dimorphous.<ref target="#foot.f1"/> Here is his first reply just in season to send to you by this post.</p>
<p>I forgot to ask him to examine <hi rend="underline">pollen</hi>. I will do so.</p>
<p>Yours ever | Asa Gray</p> 
                </div>
            </div>
        <div type="enclosure" subtype="letter" xml:id="encl.1">
      
