                    <date>May 19<hi rend="superscript">th</hi> <hi rend="print">187</hi>7</date>
                    <salute>My dear Doctor Gray.</salute>
                </opener><div type="transcription">
                     
<p>As to the dimorphism of <hi rend="underline">Lithospermum longiflorum</hi>, Spreng. or <hi rend="underline">L. angustifolium</hi> Michx. I send you measurements made upon freshly gathered specimens this morning.</p>
                    <p>I examined ten flowers from five different plants; enough to show that if there is any dimorphism it is a <hi rend="underline">wonderfully irregular one.</hi><ref target="#foot.f2"/> I copy my notes <hi rend="underline">entire.</hi></p> 

